[{"Id": 1000236, "EnglishTitle": "Dua for Protection of Faith", "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": "Imaan ki hifaazat ki dua", "UrduTitle": "ایمان کی حفاظت کی دُعا", "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1015152, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Sheikh Kulaini has narrated it from Imam Sadiq (a) how excellent the expression. It is incumbent for the man to be in occultation, I said for what? He said pointing to his stomach, he is scared, that is the awaiting one. He who people shall be in doubt of his birthday, some people shall say he is not pregnant, some shall say his father died without leaving behind a successor while some shall say he was born two years before the advent of his father. Zurarah said: I said to Imam; what will you command me to do if I reach that time? He (a) said: Offer the following supplication…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Shaikh Kulaini Janabe Zurarah se ek hadees naql karne ke zimn mein Hazrat Imam Sadiq (a) se riwaayat naql karte hai keh Hazrat ne farmaya; Us jawan ke liye har surat mein ghaibat hai, ham ne arz kiya; kyu’n ghaibat mein jaayenge? Hazrat (a) ne farmaya; khouf ki bina par (phir apne shikam-e-mubarak ki taraf ishara farmaya yaani qatl hone ke khouf se woh hai jin ke sabhi muntazir hai woh hai jin ki wilaadat ke mutaaliq log shak o shuba paiyda karte hai, baaz kehte hai abhi wilaadat nahi huwi hai, baaz kehte hai unke waaledain duniya se rukhsat huwe aur unka koi farzand is duniya mein baaqi nahi raha aur baaz kehte hai apne waalid ki wafaat se do (2) saal pehle mutawallid huwe. Zurarah ne farmaya; is dua ke zariye Khuda se talab karo…", "UrduDescription": "شیخ کلینی ؒاور دیگر بزرگان نے امام جعفر صادق ؑ سے روایت کی ہے کہ آپ ؑنے زرارہ کو یہ دعا تعلیم فرمائی : ہمارے شیعہ امام العصر(عج) کی غیبت میں اور اپنے اس امتحان میں ان کی کشائش وآسائش کے لئے یہ دعا پڑھا کریں۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1000237, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah introduce Yourself to me For, if you do not introduce Yourself to me, I will not recognize Your Prophet (s.a.w.a). O Allah make me recognize Your Prophet (s.a.w.a) because if I do not recognize Your Prophet (s.a.w.a), I will not recognize Your Proof [Imam (as)]. O Allah make me recognize Your Proof [Imam (a.s)] because if you do not make me recognize Your Proof, I will deviate from my religion.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Tu mujhe apni maarefat ataa farma, pas (is mein koi shak nahi keh) agar Tu ne mujhe apni maarefat na di to mai Tere Rasool (s.a.w.a) ko nahi pehchaan paaunga. Ay Ma’bood! Mujhe apne Rasool (s.a.w.a) ki maarefat ataa farma, pas (is mein koi shak nahi keh) agar Tu ne mujhe apne Rasool (s.a.w.a) ki maarefat ataa na ki to mai Tere Hujjat ko nahi pehchaan paaunga. Ay Ma’bood! Mujhe apne Hujjat ki maarefat ataa farma, pas be-shak agar Tu ne mujhe apne Hujjat ki maarefat na karaayi to mai apne deen se bhatak (dur ho) jaawunga.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! تو مجھے اپنی معرفت عطا کر کہ یقیناً اگر تو نے مجھے اپنی معرفت عطا نہ فرمائی تو میں تیرے رسولؐ کو نہ پہچان پاؤں گا۔ اے معبود! مجھے اپنے رسول ؐکی معرفت عطا کر کہ یقیناً اگر تو نے مجھے اپنے رسول ؐکی معرفت نہ کرائی تو میں تیری حجت ؑکو نہ پہچان پاؤں گا۔ اے معبود! مجھے اپنی حجت کی معرفت عطا کر کہ اگر تو نے مجھے اپنی حجت کی پہچان نہ کرائی تو میں اپنے دین سے گمراہ ہو جاؤں گا۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA A’RRIF-NEE NAF-SAKA, FA-INNA-KA ILLAM TO-A’RRIF-NEE NAF-SAKA LAM A’RAF RASOOLA-KA. ALLAAHUMMA A’RRIF-NEE RASOOLA-KA, FA-INNA-KA ILLAM TO-A’RRIF-NEE RASOOLA-KA LAM A’RAF HUJJATA-KA. ALLAAHUMMA A’RRIF-NEE HUJJATA-KA FA-INNA-KA ILLAM TO-A’RRIF-NEE HUJJATA-KA, ZALAL-TO A’N DEENEE.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ عَرِّفْنِيْ نَفْسَكَ، فَإِنَّكَ إِنْ لَمْ تُعَرِّفْنِيْ نَفْسَكَ لَمْ أَعْرِفْ رَسُولَكَ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ عَرِّفْنِيْ رَسُوْلَكَ فَإِنَّكَ إِنْ لَمْ تُعَرِّفْنِي رَسُوْلَكَ لَمْ أَعْرِفْ حُجَّتَكَ۔‏ اَللّٰهُمَّ عَرِّفْنِيْ حُجَّتَكَ فَإِنَّكَ إِنْ لَمْ تُعَرِّفْنِيْ حُجَّتَكَ ضَلَلْتُ عَنْ دِيْنِيْ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicG